 2020-02502020-04-10,  CIRNAC,  ,  , 
ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectWood Mountain Lakota First Nation of Reserve Land Specific Claim Settlement Agreement
PrecisOrder (1) authorizing the Minister of Crown-Indigenous Relations to enter into and execute, on behalf of Her Majesty in right of Canada, the WOOD MOUNTAIN LAKOTA FIRST NATION ALENATION OF RESERVE LAND SETTLEMENT AGREEMENT between Canada and the Wood Mountain Lakota First Nation; and (2) accepting the absolute surrender to Canada of all rights and interests of the lands.
